name: Honey I like your taste
description:
he said "honey I like your taste" 
" But you hurt me"

by the way, I'm inspired by " Beauty and The Beast ", Beauty and the beast are my inspiration to make this art, we know this story (Disney version) is full of romance. But my version of this story was that a beast could not distinguish love between obese, so He didn't realize that he hurt her till he died. 

"This is valentines day why did you make a horror story?" 
" maybe you can in love with a person who make you die"
anyway happy valentine untuk para jomblo hehe
